original: Eklundh, Anna, tandläkare, Motala, f. 22/9/80 i V. Stenby, östergötl. 1., av lantbr:ing. Teodor E. o. Hilda Vilhelmina Svensson. — Mog:ex. v. Lv-ceum f. fl. i Sthlm 99, tandl :kand. tandl. 03. Prakt, i Motala sed. 03.
translated: Eklundh, Anna, dentist, Motala, born September 22, 1880 in Västra Stenby, Östergötland, daughter of farmer Teodor E. and Hilda Vilhelmina Svensson. Attended several schools in Stockholm, graduating from Lv-ceum in 1899 and receiving a degree in dentistry in 1903. Practiced as a dentist in Motala since 1903. Married (date not specified).
